’d like to pass with your placement. These can be referenced within the rules","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of your campaign. Keys beginning with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$"},{"text":" are reserved for Superwall and will be dropped. Values can be any","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"JSON encodable value, URLs or Dates. Arrays and dictionaries as values are not supported at this time, and will","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"be dropped.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"paywallOverrides","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallOverrides"},{"type":"text","text":" object whose parameters override the paywall defaults. Use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to override products and whether it ignores the subscription status. Defaults to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"onRequestDismiss","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An optional completion block that gets called when the paywall should dismiss. This defaults to ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and the SDK","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"will call ","type":"text"},{"code":"presentationMode.wrappedValue.dismiss()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" by default. Otherwise you must perform the dismissal of the paywall.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"onSkippedView","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block that accepts a "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallSkippedReason"},{"type":"text","text":" and returns an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":". This will show"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when the requested paywall is skipped. Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EmptyView()"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"name":"feature","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block containing a feature that you wish to paywall. Access to this block is remotely configurable via the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/superwall.com\/dashboard","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". If the paywall is set to "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Non Gated","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", this will be called when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the paywall is dismissed or if the user is already paying. If the paywall is "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Gated","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", this will be called only if the user is already paying"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or if they begin paying. If no paywall is configured, this gets called immediately. This will not be called in the event of an error."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This uses "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/Superwall\/getPaywall(forPlacement:params:paywallOverrides:delegate:)","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" under the hood."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"warning","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You’re responsible for the deallocation of this view. If you have a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" presented somewhere"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and you try to present the same "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" elsewhere, you will get a crash."}]}],"name":"Warning"}],"